title: Breakingviews TV: WeWork junk
text:
Breakingviews TV: WeWork junk Thursday, April 26, 2018 - 04:47
Rob Cyran and Richard Beales share a space talking about WeWork’s $700 million junk-rated bond issue and wonder why the cash-burning upstart wants debt at all – and why investors are willing to provide it.
